g.title: j676779201
g.text: Everybody thinks I'm in charge. Nope. I'm just the one they listen to. She's the real heart of the team.

g.title: j582289838
g.text: We'd all be long dead without her. Including me. Shit, mostly me.

g.title: j3613512297
g.text: How long have you known each other?

g.title: j265975785
g.text: Way back. We served together in the ICR. She's my best mate. Couldn't do any of this nonsense without her.

g.title: j4287858458
g.text: I guess this is just me asking, in a round about way... if you're single.

g.title: j1132492464
g.text: Some things aren't your business, you know.

g.title: j1271394838
g.text: Me? I thought this was about Aoi.

g.title: j493007670
g.text: International Crisis Response. The "peace keeping" unit that got us into this shithole mess.

g.title: j3560430993
g.text: She was just a decoy, I'm really more interested in you.

g.title: j3182732262
g.text: I figured if I came out and asked you if *you* were single, you'd march over here and punch me.

g.title: j3671996383
g.text: Uh oh looks like I need to do a forced software update might loose conne -- [End.]

g.title: j1556824500
g.text: You'll have to take that up with her.

g.title: j1996893580
g.text: Never pictured you for a flirt.

g.title: j275173580
g.text: We've been friends for a long time. Closer for longer than that.

g.title: j2137363222
g.text: Be sure not to be wearing a whole lot of metal near any important bits when you do.

g.title: j249144820
g.text: Does the flirting bother you? I'll stop if it does.

g.title: j451836924
g.text: I haven't had a lot of practice, so I'm pretty bad at it, I know.

g.title: j2607655479
g.text: You don't have to tell me if you don't *want* to.

g.title: j1618774436
g.text: But if you're itching to ask more about our past, I'm going to have to stop you here. It isn't my story to tell.

g.title: j1575032799
g.text: Oh good, I'm a target dummy.

g.title: j3196084497
g.text: Like you wouldn't be able to figure it out, given enough time. We all live in the same bloody mall.

g.title: j3901814361
g.text: You'll have to ask her about it. But I'll warn you.

g.title: j1388402311
g.text: If it really bothered me, you'd know. Trust me.

g.title: j2396930189
g.text: But if you've got to make an arse out of yourself, do it here. No need to make a fool of yourself in front of the others.

g.title: j1245821567
g.text: Great! I mean, oh, what a shame.

g.title: j4161838211
g.text: Just don't be wearing a whole lot of metal near any important body parts when you do.

g.title: j201869225
g.text: Hah. Just. Let me ask. On the stubborn scale of 1 to 10, how screwed am I?

g.title: j3557244932
g.text: I'm going to run you down like a kubrodon hunting a pobber on the Venusian plains.

g.title: j1988293707
g.text: It's not serious. You're just too much fun to tease.

g.title: j2595275116
g.text: If I had any clue what literally any of that meant, I might know how to react.

g.title: j1461800772
g.text: Get in the queue with everybody else.

g.title: j807841805
g.text: So I guess I'll take it as a compliment and move on.
